  <text xml:lang="la">
    <body>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0001">
        <pb n="[110]"/>Indicis a summo capiens exordia primus,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0002">In minimi primo flexu postrema reponit,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0003">Quae sedes stat principium finisque secundi.</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0004">Tertius a summo rursum capit indicis ortum,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0005">In summo finem distinguens auricularis,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0006">Hic caput et finis quarti dinoscitur esse.</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0007">Indicis in medio quintus sumit caput artu,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0008">Et medici finem modulaminis aptat in ungue,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0009">Qui locus exortum sexti finemque tuetur.</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0010">Indicis hinc radix septeni perficit ortum,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0011">Summus apex medii cuius postrema resumit,</p>
      <p xml:id="ANOVERS0012">Octavus hac sede caput finemque reponit.</p>
    </body>
